com.github.fge.filesystem.readonly

Class ReadOnlyFileSystem

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.FileSystem
      • com.github.fge.filesystem.readonly.ReadOnlyFileSystem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class ReadOnlyFileSystem
extends FileSystem
    Read only wrapper over an existing FileSystem

    This wrapper delegates all methods to the filesystem provided as an argument except for two:

    • isReadOnly() will always return true;
    • provider() will return the delegate's provider wrapped into a ReadOnlyFileSystemProvider.
